organization_seo_description: Découvrez des soins personnalisés adaptés chez Kinatex Sports Physio. Fort d'une expertise spécifique dans plus de 60 cliniques depuis 1982.
organization_short_description:
Founded in 1982, Kinatex Sports Physio is a pioneer institution in physical therapy in the province of Quebec. Ever since its inception, the Kinatex banner has skyrocketed with a total of 32 clinics to this day and nearly 300 health employees from all walks of the trade. Kinatex operates in Montréal, La Montérégie, Lanaudière, Les Laurentides, Laval, and Québec.

Our greatest strength lies in the centralized structure of our organization, which allows us to provide professional support to each of our clinics, be it at the human resources, financial, or information technology level. The Continuing Education Committee helps our health professionals participate in conferences and workshops on industry best practices.

Our motivation, performance, skills and efforts are all focused on striving for excellence, which has allowed us to gain undisputable notoriety recognized both by the general public and high-level athletes and sports groups. Thanks to these achievements, Kinatex Sports Physio has become the official clinic for several sports organizations, namely:

•	Les Grands Ballets Canadiens de Montréal (since 1993)
•	Montreal Impact (from 1996 to 2003 and from 2008 to date)
•	Tennis Canada (since 1989)
•	Le Défi sportif (since 1990).

Since its creation, several associations, organizations, and sports groups have also partnered with Kinatex for the provision of health care to their athletes.

Kinatex consistently strives for excellence through a steady growth in the number of its branches and high quality standards, all while being recognized as an employer of choice by the best health professionals in the industry. To learn more about the expertise of our medical professionals, we invite you to browse our website: http://www.kinatex.com/en/TheGroup/OurTeam

organization_short_description:
The Lapointe Group is a company that sets up dental centres, providing the professionals practicing dentistry in their facilities with the infrastructure needed to support their practice as well as the administrative management of the centres' support staff. The Lapointe Group currently operates 16 dental centres across the province.

The professionals working in our centres, which are administered by Lapointe Dental Centres, are self-employed. They enjoy the benefits of a network, including being able to pool their expertise in the context of a multidisciplinary practice.

The Lapointe Group's core concept of integrated care consists of making a full range of dental services available under one roof to maximize patient comfort and satisfaction.

Why join the LAPOINTE GROUP?
For dental professionals, our business model offers significant advantages. Benefiting from our facilities lets you focus on your patients without having to worry about investing the time and money needed to manage your own clinic. The Group is structured to provide turnkey services that allow you to develop your practice in line with your desires and ambitions.

organization_short_description:
Herbalife is a global health and wellness community born to support you in living your best life. For over 40 years and in more than 90 countries, we've empowered millions of people to make real changes to their lives with our science-backed products, the support of a coach – what we call an Herbalife Distributor – and the opportunity to build a business. And we're just getting started.

To us, the best lives are balanced lives. Through our Herbalife Distributors, who foster community, personal growth and business opportunities to help you thrive, we offer a wide range of products designed to help you meet your needs and reach your goals. You bring the will to get started, and we'll help you every step of the way.

Herbalife's focus on improving communities inspires people to come work for us. Our 11,000+ global employees play a crucial role in realizing Herbalife's passion for helping people. 

Herbalife has been recognized with numerous global employer awards, including Achiever's Elite 8 of the Top 50 Most Engaged 8 Workplaces in 2018 and 2021, Achiever's Top 50 Most Engaged Workplaces in 2019, and Best Employers for Women by Forbes in 2020.

organization_short_description:
Founded in 1982, Kinatex Sports Physio is a pioneer institution in physical therapy in the province of Quebec. Ever since its inception, the Kinatex banner has skyrocketed with a total of 32 clinics to this day and nearly 300 health employees from all walks of the trade. Kinatex operates in Montréal, La Montérégie, Lanaudière, Les Laurentides, Laval, and Québec.

Our greatest strength lies in the centralized structure of our organization, which allows us to provide professional support to each of our clinics, be it at the human resources, financial, or information technology level. The Continuing Education Committee helps our health professionals participate in conferences and workshops on industry best practices.

Our motivation, performance, skills and efforts are all focused on striving for excellence, which has allowed us to gain undisputable notoriety recognized both by the general public and high-level athletes and sports groups. Thanks to these achievements, Kinatex Sports Physio has become the official clinic for several sports organizations, namely:

•	Les Grands Ballets Canadiens de Montréal (since 1993)
•	Montreal Impact (from 1996 to 2003 and from 2008 to date)
•	Tennis Canada (since 1989)
•	Le Défi sportif (since 1990).

Since its creation, several associations, organizations, and sports groups have also partnered with Kinatex for the provision of health care to their athletes.

Kinatex consistently strives for excellence through a steady growth in the number of its branches and high quality standards, all while being recognized as an employer of choice by the best health professionals in the industry. To learn more about the expertise of our medical professionals, we invite you to browse our website: http://www.kinatex.com/en/TheGroup/OurTeam

L'HISTOIRE DERRIÈRE DOYLE:

En décembre 1978, l'optométriste Dr. Luc Doyle fonde Doyle au cœur
du quartier historique Saint-Henri à Montréal. L'entreprise familiale
opère toujours sa boutique rue Notre-Dame et y accueille les
clients depuis plus de 40 ans. Aujourd'hui, avec ses 22 ateliers-boutiques
ayant pignon sur rue au Québec, l'entreprise a su conserver la
vision originale de docteur Doyle : participer à la vitalité du
quartier, tout en s'assurant de bien servir et représenter ses résidants.

À PROPOS DE NOUS:

Doyle renouvelle sans cesse son engagement envers l'optométrie
personnalisée et comprend plus que jamais le rôle unique des
lunettes, à la fois accessoire fonctionnel et déclaration de style
intimement lié à celui qui les porte. Avec son service à la clientèle
hors pair, son vaste choix de montures des marques les plus
prestigieuses aux plus créatives, notamment sa marque maison
Atelier 78, Doyle mise sur la qualité sans compromis.

NOTRE MISSION:

Nous souhaitons devenir la référence de l'expérience client en optique et en optométrie au Québec. Depuis 1978, le groupe Doyle développe, commercialise et assure la gestion de boutiques visuelles dont le cœur des préoccupations se situe au niveau d'un SERVICE personnalisé et compétent, de PRODUITS design, novateurs et de qualité dans un ENVIRONNEMENT raffiné et confortable. Everwell, comment ça fonctionne? 
Tout d'abord, à l'aide de notre première évaluation gratuite, nous prenons le temps d'analyser ensemble tes objectifs et les défis qui se dressent devant toi afin de pouvoir établir ensemble un plan de match solide. Nous sommes tes alliés dans un processus bâti sur mesure pour ton mode de vie.

📌 Étape 1 : On te laisse choisir ton coach parmi les meilleurs entraineurs au Québec. Atteins la meilleure version de toi-même à l'aide du suivi de consultation le plus personnalisé, même à distance.

📌 Étape 2: Obtiens une analyse complète de ta condition physique grâce à la technologie InBody? Offerte dans six succursales Popeye's Suppléments à travers le Québec, InBody nous permet de calculer ton taux de gras, ta rétention d'eau, ton métabolisme de base et bien plus. Fini les pincettes! Retire tes souliers, grimpe sur l'appareil et obtiens les données de composition corporelle les plus précises sur le marché.
➤Popeye's: Laval, Longueuil, Pointe-Claire, Saint-Léonard, Québec et Trois-Rivières.

📌 Étape 3: Retrouve tes plans d'entraînements et ta structure santé physique à un seul endroit: L'application mobile Everwell. Disponible sur ton cellulaire et sur ta montre intelligente, tu peux accéder à tout tes plans et discuter avec ton coach directement sur la messagerie privée! En tant qu'alliés, nous sommes à ton écoute 24/7.

Pour ton évaluation gratuite, c'est par ici : https://go.everwellpro.com/everwell-consultation-gratuite/

Our clinic has the top Neuroscientists, Neuropsychologists, Physiotherapists, and Specialists who share the same passion in assisting all our clients to live their best healthy and happy life. 
The mission of our clinic is to improve the quality of life of children and adults suffering from functional neurological disorders such as ADD/ADHD, depression, head trauma, stroke, cerebral palsy, multiple sclerosis, Parkinson's Disease, Alzheimer's Disease, and other neurological conditions.
Our experts help restore functions beyond traditionally expected boundaries as we propose state-of-the-art scientific techniques and advanced technologies.

organization_short_description:
Fitness AI is a mobile app that uses artificial intelligence (AI) to help users get fit and healthy. The app can be used to create personalized workout plans, track progress, and stay motivated.

Our Vision

We envision a world where everyone is healthy and fit. We believe that AI can make fitness more accessible and effective, and we are committed to working with the fitness community to make it happen.

Our Mission

Our mission is to make it easy for everyone to get fit and healthy. We do this by providing a user-friendly app that anyone can use, regardless of their fitness level or experience.

How It Works

The Fitness AI App works by asking the user a few questions about their fitness goals and preferences. The app then uses AI to create a personalized workout plan that is tailored to the user's individual needs. The app also tracks the user's progress and provides feedback, so they can stay motivated and on track.

Features

The Fitness AI App includes the following features:

    Personalized workout plans: The app creates personalized workout plans that are tailored to the user's individual needs.
    Progress tracking: The app tracks the user's progress and provides feedback, so they can stay motivated and on track.
    Motivational features: The app includes motivational features, such as progress streaks and challenges, to help users stay motivated.

Pricing

The Fitness AI App is free to download and use. The app also offers a premium subscription that unlocks additional features, such as access to more workout plans and more detailed progress tracking.

How to Get Started

To get started with the Fitness AI App, simply download the app from the App Store or Google Play. Once you have downloaded the app, create an account, and follow the instructions to get started.

We hope you enjoy using the Fitness AI!

organization_short_description:
Origine est un studio d'entraînement basé à l'assomption et fondé dans un désir d'offrir des entraînements performants, mais aussi réparateurs et fonctionnels, et de revenir aux bases de la motricité et de la biomécanique humaine tel que déterminée par l'évolution: Marcher, Courir et Lancer.

L'entièreté de nos entraînement se base sur la méthode novatrice FUNCTIONAL PATTERNS, qui permet à la fois de réhabiliter les blessures, de corriger la posture et les patrons de mouvement problématiques et d'optimiser la performance en respectant la Tenségrité Myofasciale (Muscles et Fascias) de votre corps. Vous rendre plus efficacement et optimalement humain, en quelque sorte. 

Nous offrons des cours de groupes de boxe et d'entrainement fonctionnel évolutif ainsi que de l'entrainement privé. La formule d'entrainement est basée sur functional patterns et notre studio est le premier au Québec à offrir ce type de conditionnement physique. Celui-ci vise à optimiser les fonctions biomécaniques de base : courir, sauter, et lancer. Il permet de réduire les compressions articulaires et réduire, voir éliminer les douleurs chroniques. 

L'entrainement chez Origine est disponibles sour forme d'Entraînement en Groupe (FIX, EVO , BOXE), d'Entraînement privé (réadaptation et performance), et d'Encadrement Athlétique (planification et programmation). Nos entraînement permettent de:

-Gérer et résorber les douleurs à l'entraînement
-Optimiser la composition corporelle en diminuant le % de graisse et en augmentant la masse musculaire
-Maintenir un niveau d'énergie optimal grâce à l'optimisation métabolique de notre méthode et de notre environnement de travail (Le studio)
-Développer votre confiance et Gérer la composante myofascial du stress et obtenir un défoulement exutoire
-Augmenter l'énergie globale
-Apprendre à bouger au quotidien efficacement
-Être plus athlétique
-Optimiser vos performances sportives
-Vieillir de plus en plus jeune

Le tout, sans douleur.

organization_seo_description: Ma mission : Offrir un environnement de travail confortable et sécuritaire pour les travailleurs.
organization_short_description:
Ergonovix offers cutting-edge ergonomic services including expert solutions such as the design of virtual ergonomic computer-aided design (CAD) solutions with the use of the Human Digital Model (DHM).

Ergonovix offers user-centered design services and universal design according to the anthropometries specific to each population such as remote populations and the aging population.

Ergonovix specializes in systemic analyzes in Human Factors, in-depth analyzes for the Government, Manufacturing and Aerospace sector by respecting standards and guides leading to certification and / or compliance with good practices.

Ergonovix offers innovative project management with unique programs aimed at improving employee well-being by reducing costs associated with musculoskeletal injuries (MSDs) and improving your employer brand.

Retire tes souliers, grimpe sur l'appareil et obtiens les données de composition corporelle les plus précises sur le marché.
➤Popeye's: Laval, Longueuil, Pointe-Claire, Saint-Léonard, Québec et Trois-Rivières.

Ever since its inception, the Kinatex banner has skyrocketed with a total of 32 clinics to this day and nearly 300 health employees from all walks of the trade. Kinatex operates in Montréal, La Montérégie, Lanaudière, Les Laurentides, Laval, and Québec.

Our greatest strength lies in the centralized structure of our organization, which allows us to provide professional support to each of our clinics, be it at the human resources, financial, or information technology level. The Continuing Education Committee helps our health professionals participate in conferences and workshops on industry best practices.

Our motivation, performance, skills and efforts are all focused on striving for excellence, which has allowed us to gain undisputable notoriety recognized both by the general public and high-level athletes and sports groups. Thanks to these achievements, Kinatex Sports Physio has become the official clinic for several sports organizations, namely:

•	Les Grands Ballets Canadiens de Montréal (since 1993)
•	Montreal Impact (from 1996 to 2003 and from 2008 to date)
•	Tennis Canada (since 1989)
•	Le Défi sportif (since 1990).

Since its creation, several associations, organizations, and sports groups have also partnered with Kinatex for the provision of health care to their athletes.

Kinatex consistently strives for excellence through a steady growth in the number of its branches and high quality standards, all while being recognized as an employer of choice by the best health professionals in the industry. Les magasins affiliés idéalement situés sont détenus et exploités par des pharmaciens-propriétaires agréés qui ont aidé le franchiseur Shoppers Drug Mart/Pharmaprix à bâtir une marque synonyme de service, de valeur et de confiance exceptionnels.

organization_short_description:
Founded in 1982, Kinatex Sports Physio is a pioneer institution in physical therapy in the province of Quebec. Ever since its inception, the Kinatex banner has skyrocketed with a total of 32 clinics to this day and nearly 300 health employees from all walks of the trade. Kinatex operates in Montréal, La Montérégie, Lanaudière, Les Laurentides, Laval, and Québec.

Our greatest strength lies in the centralized structure of our organization, which allows us to provide professional support to each of our clinics, be it at the human resources, financial, or information technology level. The Continuing Education Committee helps our health professionals participate in conferences and workshops on industry best practices.

Our motivation, performance, skills and efforts are all focused on striving for excellence, which has allowed us to gain undisputable notoriety recognized both by the general public and high-level athletes and sports groups. Thanks to these achievements, Kinatex Sports Physio has become the official clinic for several sports organizations, namely:

•	Les Grands Ballets Canadiens de Montréal (since 1993)
•	Montreal Impact (from 1996 to 2003 and from 2008 to date)
•	Tennis Canada (since 1989)
•	Le Défi sportif (since 1990).

Since its creation, several associations, organizations, and sports groups have also partnered with Kinatex for the provision of health care to their athletes.

Kinatex consistently strives for excellence through a steady growth in the number of its branches and high quality standards, all while being recognized as an employer of choice by the best health professionals in the industry. To learn more about the expertise of our medical professionals, we invite you to browse our website: http://www.kinatex.com/en/TheGroup/OurTeam

Carebook's family of global solutions, CoreHealth and Wellness Checkpoint, power advanced digital health solutions that bring together the science of prevention, the art of engagement, and the power of technology to support people on their health journeys—every step of the way.

Collectively, the Carebook family supports the health and well-being of over 3.5 million lives in more than 100 countries globally.

Today, we bring together the most comprehensive and customized end-to-end health and wellness platform and suite of solutions for employers, wellness providers, insurance providers, and more.  

At Carebook, we believe in a world of connected, integrated health where people are empowered and supported on their health journeys.

Based in Montreal, Carebook's philosophy is people-first, and our goal is accessible, connected health for everyone.

Chez Physio Atlas, la mission est d'offrir à nos patients les meilleurs soins de physiothérapie en mettant le bien-être et les attentes de ceux-ci au centre de notre approche thérapeutique.

Faire la différence dans la vie des gens a toujours été une priorité. Notre prise en charge en salle fermée nous permet d'aborder les problèmes en profondeur et de créer un lien thérapeutique fort et efficace. Physio Atlas offre depuis ses débuts un service professionnel de physiothérapie : les séances de traitement individuel sont faites exclusivement par des physiothérapeutes. Nos traitements combinent la thérapie manuelle, les exercices spécifiques et les modalités appropriées afin d'optimiser le retour aux activités normales.

Le développement professionnel des physiothérapeutes est au cœur de l'entreprise. Nous encourageons une pratique basée sur les évidences scientifiques. Favoriser et accélérer le développement de l'expertise des physiothérapeutes est essentiel afin d'assurer un haut niveau de performance et de satisfaction des patients.

name: Vincent Zourikian
title: Owner Principal
headline: Personal trainer
organization_short_description:
Fitness AI is a mobile app that uses artificial intelligence (AI) to help users get fit and healthy. The app can be used to create personalized workout plans, track progress, and stay motivated.

Our Vision

We envision a world where everyone is healthy and fit. We believe that AI can make fitness more accessible and effective, and we are committed to working with the fitness community to make it happen.

Our Mission

Our mission is to make it easy for everyone to get fit and healthy. We do this by providing a user-friendly app that anyone can use, regardless of their fitness level or experience.

How It Works

The Fitness AI App works by asking the user a few questions about their fitness goals and preferences. The app then uses AI to create a personalized workout plan that is tailored to the user's individual needs. The app also tracks the user's progress and provides feedback, so they can stay motivated and on track.

Features

The Fitness AI App includes the following features:

    Personalized workout plans: The app creates personalized workout plans that are tailored to the user's individual needs.
    Progress tracking: The app tracks the user's progress and provides feedback, so they can stay motivated and on track.
    Motivational features: The app includes motivational features, such as progress streaks and challenges, to help users stay motivated.

Pricing

The Fitness AI App is free to download and use. The app also offers a premium subscription that unlocks additional features, such as access to more workout plans and more detailed progress tracking.

How to Get Started

To get started with the Fitness AI App, simply download the app from the App Store or Google Play. Once you have downloaded the app, create an account, and follow the instructions to get started.

We hope you enjoy using the Fitness AI!
